<main>

Let’s pause here for a second. Sit down if you like. Catch your breath. Peaceful, isn’t it? Nice to see a bit of green around here. Don’t think we had this place when I was knocking about. Lucky you. Hang about, who’s this? Two men? They look a bit fancy, don’t they? Look, I can’t be recognised, so you’ll need to eavesdrop on them for me. Act natural — whatever that means to you.

Apparently she hangs around here. If we’re lucky, maybe she’ll cut our purse-strings.

Wouldn’t that be good? First hand experience.

You know, I’m still struggling with the ending. Surely she should be married off?

Moll Cutpurse? Married off? Never. She wouldn’t allow it. It would be a betrayal.

But the audience will be in uproar!

Don’t be so old-fashioned. As long as we have one wedding in there, we’ll be safe.

Hey! I can’t hear. Who’re they talking about?


